	<h1 class="title">因为麦当劳，蒂姆·波顿就没再拍过《蝙蝠侠》？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-25 15:00:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4700/medium/4700.jpeg?1436651957" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="4700" data-title="《因为麦当劳，蒂姆·波顿就没再拍过《蝙蝠侠》？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/4700/medium/4700.jpeg?1436651957" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/4700.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
